File libsrc/libcssio/readTables.c

Routines for reading and writing CSS formatted ascii records. CSS3.0 data structures are used. (ARRIVAL30, WFDISC30, etc.)

(For an alternative CSS I/O library see libgobject.)

See Also:
CssTable_readFile
